OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FStormont minister          
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'concerned' at PSNI Pride  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fstance                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Police Service of Northern Ireland 
OL,6, (PSNI) risks its relationship with the 
OL,7, LGBT community "slipping backwards", a 
OL,8, Stormont minister has said.            
OL,10,FAndrew Muir, who is gay, was speaking  
OL,11,Fas part of a BBC Spotlight programme   
OL,12,Finto the murder of a police officer.   
OL,14,FHe said not allowing officers to take  
OL,15,Fpart in the 2023 Belfast Pride parade  
OL,16,Fin uniform was "concerning".           
OL,18,FThe PSNI said the decision was taken to
OL,19,Fcomply with its obligations on         
OL,20,Fimpartiality.                          
